6 distributions, and the acceptance of rollovers;
7 (h) To obtain auditing services for a separate compliance audit of
8 the retirement systems to be completed by December 31, 2028, and from
9 time to time at the request of the Nebraska Retirement Systems Committee
10 of the Legislature, to be completed not more than every four years but
11 not less than every ten years. The compliance audit shall be in addition
12 to the annual audit conducted by the Auditor of Public Accounts. The
13 compliance audit shall include, but not be limited to, an examination of
