5 Department of State;
6 (f) A United States passport;
7 (g) A foreign passport with a United States visa;
8 (h) A United States Certificate of Naturalization;
9 (i) A United States Certificate of Citizenship;
10 (j) A tribal certificate of Native American blood or similar
11 document;
12 (k) A United States Citizenship and Immigration Services Employment
